    date: "2024-01-15",
    slug: "getting-started-with-astro"
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    title: "Building with Tailwind CSS",
    excerpt: "How utility-first CSS frameworks can speed up your development workflow.",
    date: "2024-01-10",
    slug: "building-with-tailwind-css"
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    title: "JavaScript Modern Patterns",
    excerpt: "Exploring contemporary JavaScript patterns and best practices for 2024.",
    date: "2024-01-05",
    slug: "javascript-modern-patterns"
  },
  {
    id: 4,
    title: "Web Performance Optimization",
    excerpt: "Techniques and strategies to make your websites load faster and perform better.",
    date: "2024-01-01",
    slug: "web-performance-optimization"
  },
  {
    id: 5,
    title: "TypeScript for Better Code",
    excerpt: "How TypeScript can improve your development experience and code quality.",
    date: "2023-12-28",
    slug: "typescript-for-better-code"
  },
  {
